commitmsg:
Merge pull request #43 from keianhzo/unzip_refactor

Remove speechlibrary dependency from utils
Run local STT in a different thread
Make mozillaspeechlibrary compileOnly and other fixes
Added support for using GeckoWebExecutor when available
Call cancel on the network thread too when calling cancel on the service

Add Mozilla Code of Conduct file

Fixes #10.

_(Message COC002)_

Switch to VOICE_RECOGNITION audio source

Testing shows it's uncovering much better results, especially running
with DeepSpeech in crowed / noisy environment
Make the library compatible with java 1.7
Make toogles on in the default app
Adding new headers to support multi-lingual, turn on/off the storing of samples and transcriptions, a tag name for the client
Making the demo app hardware accelerated to better render the decibels graph
Update Idle state even when there are no listeners attached
